{"word":"Elisha","slug":"elisha","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Elisha</b> - successor of the prophet Elijah<p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=16'>1Ki 19:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=19'>1Ki 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=2'>2Ki 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=12'>2Ki 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=24'>2Ki 2:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=13'>2Ki 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=2'>2Ki 4:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=8'>2Ki 4:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=32'>2Ki 4:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=38'>2Ki 4:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=8'>2Ki 5:8</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=1'>2Ki 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=7&verse=1'>2Ki 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=1'>2Ki 8:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=1'>2Ki 9:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=14'>2Ki 13:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=21'>2Ki 13:21</a><p/><b>(2) A \"Model Spiritual Leader\"</b><p/>A man of great energy<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=19'>1Ki 19:19</a><p/>When called, made a complete surrender<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=20'>1Ki 19:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=21'>1Ki 19:21</a><p/>Sought a spiritual equipment<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=9'>2Ki 2:9</a><p/>Spoke with authority, as the oracle of God<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=16'>2Ki 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=17'>2Ki 3:17</a><p/>Put his entire personality into the work<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=34'>2Ki 4:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=35'>2Ki 4:35</a><p/>Was of incorruptible integrity<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=16'>2Ki 5:16</a><p/>Lived in the spirit of victory<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=15'>2Ki 6:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=16'>2Ki 6:16</a><p/>A man of spiritual vision<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=17'>2Ki 6:17</a><p/>Died a victorious death<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=14'>2Ki 13:14-19</a><p/>Had a wonderful posthumous influence<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=20'>2Ki 13:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=21'>2Ki 13:21</a><p/>---, Miracles of. <b>SEE</b> Miracles, MIRACLES"}]}